906
00:55:17,260 --> 00:55:19,890
[What?]

907
00:55:20,990 --> 00:55:23,220
[Water gun!]

908
00:55:26,520 --> 00:55:29,800
[That is without a doubt, a water gun!]

909
00:55:41,460 --> 00:55:45,210
