923
00:57:03,840 --> 00:57:06,830
This is just total entrapment.

924
00:57:06,830 --> 00:57:09,180
[Entrapment?]

925
00:57:11,290 --> 00:57:12,740
Who is it?

926
00:57:13,760 --> 00:57:15,330
Who could it be?

927
00:57:16,330 --> 00:57:18,310
